des: If you're a founder of a company or would like to start a company one day, you need a boost of daily motivation. Start your day with an inspirational list of quotes by founders who have been there, done that. They have a piece of wisdom to share in order inspire you to move forward with gusto and enthusiasm.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
